bpedia.org/resource/Ada_Choi\", \"score\": 0.9999961232558802, \"rank\": 3.8767590731976754e-06, \"text\": \"Choi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ada_Choi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ada_Choi\"}, {\"begin\": 3465, \"end\": 3470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_City\", \"score\": 0.9873562612438554, \"rank\": 0.012805627671302215, \"text\": \"Logan\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3448}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3499}, {\"ngram\": \"two top breakers\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, Dominika Banevic of Lithuania, Say Dembele of France, and Ayumi Fukushima of Japan are expected to put forth strong appearances.\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3555, \"end\": 3564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9998082107557064, \"rank\": 0.00019182463035091345, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3581, \"end\": 3587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.937886595289288, \"rank\": 0.034960748734345036, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3599, \"end\": 3608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fukushima_nuclear_disaster\", \"score\": 0.999992030743592, \"rank\": 7.969254744770239e-06, \"text\": \"Fukushima\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fukushima_nuclear_disaster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbp